The paper discusses the combination of machine learning and logic in AI reasoning systems, which falls under the category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses specific methods and algorithms related to machine learning (cs.LG) and logic (cs.LO), as well as natural language processing (cs.CL) and cryptography (cs.CR) in the context of AI reasoning systems. Therefore, these are the most likely sub-categories for this paper.
